name: Homecoming
description: Voyagers and their crews - from across time and space - take on one final mission in the Delta Quadrant - to restore peace on their way home... but they'll need your help to bring their adventure to a close.
rules:
-- Unique Borg, Federation, and Maquis Faction Missions are available during the event. Open the Event to access them.
-- Using Gul Evek, any version of Mark Johnson, Paris, Janeway, or Voyager crew will provide a bonus to Event Faction Missions.
-- Every Event Faction Mission you succeed at earns you Event Victory Points. Collect Victory Points to unlock Event Threshold Rewards.
-- In this event, Squadrons may also compete to advance up the Squadron leaderboards. Join a Squadron to get more rewards!
bonus_text: Crew Bonus: Gul Evek, Mark Johnson, Paris, Janeway, or Voyager
rewards_teaser: Reach Rank 1 by gaining Victory Points from Event Missions!

featured_crew.name: Kore
featured_crew.flavor: Kore’s world is shattered when she learns she is not Dr. Adam Soong’s daughter, but one in a series of clones he created.

featured_crew.name: Paris
featured_crew.flavor: Paris loves billiards! For him, this is an opportunity to have fun and show dexterity. Well, cheat a little.

action.name: It's Just a Little Diversion, Captain

featured_crew.name: Janeway
featured_crew.flavor: Some decisions are too difficult. And despite looking stern during the separation process, Janeway can barely contain her emotions afterward.
